 you provide any personal information to dotemirates.</p>\r\n\r\n						<p>Contacting dotemirates about this Privacy Policy<br>\r\n							If you have any questions or comments about this Privacy Policy please contact us.</p>\r\n					</div>\r\n				</div>', 'privacy', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'privacy', '', '', '2018-07-09 17:46:56', '2018-07-09 14:46:56', '', 0, 'http://localhost/dot-emirates/?page_id=64', 0, 'page', '', 0),
